These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, blend, alhambra, old-henry, vegafina
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, epic, animation, disaster, satire
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, roller, snowmobile, quad-bike, airplane
5 different games are played: bridge, snooker, poker, whist, backgammon
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person driving the roller is the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Cigar         | blend  | davidoff    | old-henry | alhambra    | vegafina  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | spy | animation | disaster | satire  |
| Transport           | scooter     | airplane     | quad-bike  | roller   | snowmobile    |
| Game         | poker | whist    | snooker | bridge  | backgammon |

