.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, aconite, amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, helicopter, snowmobile, ship
5 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, may, february, december, july
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsaconite##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person who growsaconite is the person driving the boat##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Flower          | aconite        | balloon-flower | daisy     | amaryllis      | lily  |
| Transport           | boat   | helicopter | ship    | snowmobile | jet-ski |
| Pet   | chinchilla | lizard     | rabbit | cat    | ferret  |
| Birthday   | december     | may | september    | july      | february    |

