.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  photographer, dancer, chef, accountant, manager
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, green, pink, aquamarine, apricot
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, august, february, october, june
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, manager-polo, snowboarding, badminton
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
 4. the dancer is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is manager-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes ebony##1
12. the manager is on the right of the photographer##1
13. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Job      | accountant          | chef  | dancer       | photographer     | manager      |
| Color         | green | apricot | aquamarine  | pink   | ebony    |
| Birthday   | august        | june | november | october    | february   |
| Sport     | volleyball   | manager-polo | badminton      | surfing | snowboarding |

