.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince, blend, montecristo, siglo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, hot-chocolate, milk, iced-tea
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, german, american, thai, colombian
5 different games are played: backgammon, go, chess, mah-jongg, bridge
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the argentine##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the german is the person drinking cola##1
 4. the argentine is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 9. the thai is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the siglo-smoker is the american##1
11. the prince-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Cigar          | montecristo        | aristoff       | blend | prince   | siglo  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | cola | coffee   | milk |
| Nationality   | thai         | colombian     | german | argentine | american     |
| Game     | backgammon        | go        | bridge    | mah-jongg    | chess      |

