 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the blend-smoker is the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the colonial house is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the palace house is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the cottage house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the craftsman house##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Birthday          | january    | november  | june | july    | october      |
