There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water, milk, mirinda
 1. the person who likes coral is the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the police-officer##1
 3. the electrician is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who likes amber is the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the nurse##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the left of the designer##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking milk is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | dunhill  | bluemaster    | tiparillo | bolivar |
| Color   | coral        | chestnut  | amber | ivory      | azure        |
