10. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of punk##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is the person playing whist##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
