.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, april, october, july, march
City: miami, colone, liverpool, new-york, hamburg
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, lime, garlic, radish, carrot
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, poppy, amaryllis, dahlia
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the person traveling to liverpool is the person eating radish##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday      | june      | april       | march         | july  | october |
| City   | liverpool  | new-york | colone | miami  | hamburg  |
| Food   | radish    | lime    | blueberry        | carrot | garlic     |
| Flower           | aconite | poppy      | azalea       | amaryllis   | dahlia   |

