.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, subway, van, motorbike, train
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, aconite, lily, daisy
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, tower, futuristic, craftsman
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, cain, ritmeester, chaman
 1. the futuristic house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the tower house is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person driving the subway is the game-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the van is the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
10. the farmhouse house is the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who growslily##1
12. the person driving the train is on the left of the futuristic house##1
13. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Transport   | subway      | motorbike | van  | train    | airplane |
| Flower   | lily     | daisy     | sunflower | tulip      | aconite      |
| House           | tower       | farmhouse     | cape-cod     | craftsman     | futuristic   |
| Cigar         | game | ritmeester | oliveros  | chaman | cain   |

