.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, ritmeester, dunhill, vegafina
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, begonia, poppy, azalea
5 different games are played: go, scrabble, backgammon, monopoly, canasta
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, snowboarding, biathlon, sailing, climbing
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person who growsbegonia is the vegafina-smoker##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Cigar      | ritmeester | vegafina    | bluemaster   | dunhill   | pall-mall |
| Flower   | dahlia    | begonia   | azalea | poppy | rose  |
| Game           | scrabble     | monopoly | backgammon   | canasta | go   |
| Sport     | snowboarding  | climbing   | swimming    | sailing   | biathlon |

