.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, sailing, parkour, ice-hockey, rugby
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, chef, bartender, pilot, manager
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, drama, fantasy, comedy, spy
House: wooden, tower, craftsman, palace, modern
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
 2. the pilot is the wooden house##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the nurse is the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the modern house is on the far right##1
 6. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the bartender is the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the tower house is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
11. the nurse is on the far right##1
12. the manager is in the middle##1
13. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
14. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Sport      | sailing | ice-hockey   | parkour    | handball       | rugby |
| Job   | bartender           | chef   | manager   | pilot       | nurse  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama       | romance | fantasy | comedy     | spy   |
| House     | craftsman    | tower   | palace   | wooden | modern   |

 